window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A classic Ngaio Marsh novel in which a game of darts in an English pub has gruesome consequences. </p> <p>At the Plume of Feathers in south Devon one midsummer evening, eight people are gathered together in the taproom. They are in the habit of playing darts, but on this occasion an experiment takes the place of the usual game - a fatal experiment which calls for investigation. </p> <p>A distinguished painter, a celebrated actor, a woman graduate, a plump lady from County Clare, and a Devonshire farmer all play their parts in the unravelling of the problem.... </p>"; 
